metadata.name: Tears Through Her Eyes
metadata.description: If you look into the eyes of people what story does it tell? Does it tell of love, hurt, fear, comfort or regrets. The world we live in tends to forget that we are all just here to make a living for ourselves and live our best life's, don't hurt those around you for no reason, be kind and if you see sadness in their eyes be of comfort and help them out.
